product.name: Panasonic HDC-MDH 1 Professional Video
product.description: The Panasonic HDC Point & Shoot camera is a highly capable device and is also great for beginners and intermediates alike.The camera comes with a powerful 20.4 MP EXMOR R Sensor. This Panasonic HDC sensor is a great choice for high speed photography and even for low light conditions. The BIONZ image processor allows for high quality images.This camera is equipped with Carl Zeiss optics and is also supplemented with the Vario Sonnar T Lens. This arrangement is highly useful for high quality photos along a wide range of lighting conditions. The lens is capable of a zoom level that is 50 times more than the standard focus. The 100 X clear image zoom feature also augments this 50 X zoom lens.This is a feature found commonly in many cameras though most do not offer high speed auto modes. This camera however is able to support high speed auto modes that can help in times when you need to quickly takes some photographs and you are left with little or no time to manually set the values.

product.name: Nikon D5200 SLR
product.description:
Taking a picture or shooting a video is not just about saving a series of memories, you also put in a lot of your own creativity to bring the moment alive in an artificial medium which by itself is no easy task. The D5200 by Nikon is a great DSLR camera with exceptional handling and exciting new perspectives depending on the kind of lens you pair it with.
This camera is equipped with a fairly large, powerful 24.1 MP DX-format CMOS sensor that can take stunning pictures across a wide range of lighting conditions. The sensor is designed to reproduce images with stunning quality and it can also be used for high sensitivity images that require a range of ISO settings. The EXPEED 3 image processing engine works well with the intelligent scene recognition system that can automatically set the right values for a perfect shot.
